## Description {#details}

Represents flags for the getelementptr instruction/expression.

The following flags are supported:
<ul>
<li>inbounds (implies nusw)</li>
<li>nusw (no unsigned signed wrap)</li>
<li>nuw (no unsigned wrap) See LangRef for a description of their semantics.</li>
</ul>

Definition at line 26 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/gepnowrapflags-h">GEPNoWrapFlags.h</a>.
